Solution 2: Positional indexesIn the postings, store, for each term the position(s) in which tokens of it appear:

<term, number of docs containing term;
doc1: position1, position2 … ;
doc2: position1, position2 … ;
etc.>C. D. Manning, P. Raghavan and H. Schütze,  Introduction to Information Retrieval

Positional index exampleFor phrase queries, we use a merge algorithm recursively at the document level
But we now need to deal with more than just equality<be: 993427;
1: 7, 18, 33, 72, 86, 231;
2: 3, 149;
4: 17, 191, 291, 430, 434;
